{"tid":54041,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/PC]街霸V[13]Season2啟動","createTime":"2016-12-25T08:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T08:23:14.000Z","uid":64858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c979fa089793390b45d76cba9f0833fadab76d5","tid":54041,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/3h0c18y9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3h0c18y9&h=68d71256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一瞬千擊!<br />\n拔山蓋世!<br />\n鬼哭啾啾!<br />\n故豪鬼成!</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<a href=\"http://streetfighter.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstreetfighter.com%2F&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=135c1c6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://streetfighter.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n簡介:街頭霸王（日文：&amp;#12473;&amp;#12488;&amp;#12522;&amp;#12540;&amp;#12488;&amp;#12501;&amp;#12449;&amp;#12452;&amp;#12479;&amp;#12540;，英文：Street Fighter，台灣名命為「快打旋風」，在香港簡稱&ldquo;街霸&rdquo;），是由日本CAPCOM公司於1987年推出的大型電玩機台格鬥遊戲，其後推出後續版本，是一個流行的格鬥遊戲系列，也有日本動畫及歐美電影。《街頭霸王》普遍被認為雙人格鬥遊戲始祖之一，當時大型電玩機台仍以射擊或動作等單人遊戲為主，雙人對打作品並不多見。而街霸V係開發日2月16日認為街霸係一種運動. <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xuf6ezv5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxuf6ezv5&h=0eec0d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而Playstation HK最近為街霸做左唔小宣傳,例如教人打街霸.<br />\n亦有一堆YOUTUBER製作左有趣既宣傳片.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aMUAxIq5_kw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaMUAxIq5_kw&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=63a206a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aMUAxIq5_kw</a><br />\n<br />\nQ.有咩大制好介紹 <br />\nA.除左Razar,Madcatz大制之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,其他一律安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ.今集可支援PS3大制?<br />\nA.係可以的.但有部份支援唔到.<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poEoW1peNDGO6xBiThed03jI9TdY78MaFKVCm52rQ1c/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1poEoW1peNDGO6xBiThed03jI9TdY78MaFKVCm52rQ1c%2Fedit&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e788ba72\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poEoW1peNDGO6xBiThed03jI9TdY78MaFKVCm52rQ1c/edit</a><br />\nQ.請問玩格鬥GAME係咪一定要大制先生存到? <br />\nA.不,只係手制比較容易有MISTAKE,例如唔小心禁到其他制,比較難禁R2L2 <br />\n不過唔代表一定輸比大制玩家,而家EVO比賽都有人玩手制都拎到冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ.請問今集遊戲平台分別有?<br />\nA. PS4 同 PC, 而且係誇平台,所以你可以PS4打PC玩家.<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3rgXBKNov1Kuz6KMKc/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3rgXBKNov1Kuz6KMKc%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6cec9cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ.今集有咩系統更新?<br />\nA.<br />\n1.Crush Counter係由重腳OR重拳造成既COUNTER,可以幫助唔同角色製造COMBO<br />\n(如果你亂咁昇會食好多DAMGE,真係好多,同時做出CC也可以增加自己的VT)<br />\n2.每個角色有唔同既V-skill同V-trigger<br />\n3.無左SF4既Focus系統<br />\n4.V-trigger一格可以彈走人(類似拳皇果種用一條能量BAR黎彈開人)<br />\n5.0血唔會俾波屈死(大絕除外),可以無限擋,所以可以0血反CUP<br />\nQ.如何練好基本功?<br />\nA.<br />\n1.你要上網睇你角色既COMBO VIDEO<br />\n2.第二係應用VIDEO<br />\n3.你最想打敗既敵人既應用Video<br />\n4.打破心理關口.小D耐性就會輸(唔好用拳皇果種瘋狂跳去人,係街霸世界唔WORK)<br />\n5.唔好只係為左出招,多D運用基本重拳,輕拳重腳等拉距離or壓線.<br />\n6.達人落地唔係狗既行為,係戰術.<br />\n7.多D睇比賽玩家既打法,可以啟發到你玩格鬥GAME既靈感.<br />\n<br />\n呢個街霸Group係聚集打格鬥GAME既同好既地方.<br />\n唔係Show off自己實力黎踩低人既地方.<br />\n作為新手,唔好怕輸,輸左唔會拎左你條命.<br />\n輸左要反省點解輸左黎為左下一次既進步<br />\n如果你係強者,你應該要協助下新手.<br />\n而唔係屌柒新手趕人走,因為呢度唔係一言堂.<br />\n呢度係討論區.係俾人討論既地方"},{"pid":"26a214cf3c385fdc6e8afcf4c17c94502ce9d16b","tid":54041,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"12月20更新資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lecgz64b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flecgz64b&h=799397e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左會有AKUMA正式登場之外同埋己經講左5個<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>全新角色</ins></span><br />\n今次既改版將會係宇宙級大改動,<br />\n1.首先係Overhead可連技既年代.<br />\n有部分角色會受到優惠.<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ev2h4qjc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fev2h4qjc&h=4bb8f62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如Necalli既overhead(而家可以儲)<br />\n打中可以連技.<br />\nKEN既前重腳都係<br />\n其他可以做到既話就請玩家發掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.Wake Up昇不再王道.<br />\nSeason1會發現好多問題係有對空技既角色<br />\n都會有好強既Startup無敵既昇,<br />\n故此,如果你將人掃低想做meaty或者Setup你會考慮一下做防守之類.<br />\n呢個版本就改走左Startup無敵呢個(至小Frame3,有錯請指)<br />\n只有EX昇先會一開始無敵.<br />\n <img src=\"https://holland.pk/ub9rmlqf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fub9rmlqf&h=8dce4bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.將過強既MOVE大Nerf<br />\n係Season1會發現部份角色某動作過強,所以而家會NERF<br />\nA.春麗既輕腳判定<br />\nB.隆既輕拳判定<br />\nC.Necalli既輕拳判定.<br />\nD.ALEX既輕拳判定.<br />\nE.R.Mika已經唔可以再撞場(如果非牆邊)<br />\nF.Nash 前DASH後DASH都大弱<br />\n其餘請玩家自行發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4.抆線狗下一場再遇到你既機率大增<br />\n呢個唔洗解釋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/znklxs7g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fznklxs7g&h=99f6dcc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e897d7c76fce330e763f4147ef5bd8f686679945","tid":54041,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://holland.pk/0z3fboqu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0z3fboqu&h=cf3f4407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9種最基本追加教學(GAME教學無教,學到就對GAME有絕對大幫助)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wPPBuY9_ZNY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwPPBuY9_ZNY&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e9951d52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wPPBuY9_ZNY</a><br />\n關於儲氣型角色常見問題<br />\n<br />\nQ.仲有就係,我玩m. bison果時佢有招技係 左,右+拳(Psycho Blast L) <br />\n其實係要點出? 我試過 按實左, 跟住即刻右拳 係出到,但只係5次先有一次得 <br />\n我試過 左,右+拳 係唔得的 <br />\n如果 按實左, 跟住即刻右拳 ,咁連技果時咪會好慢  <br />\n所以請教各位巴打解答下我 <br />\n<br />\nA.你出唔到係chok錯野 training 果度有得開input list睇返你自已禁左咩制 <br />\n果招連技就係一開始已經拉後 一路拳腳緊果陣已經儲緊氣 唔係到出果陣先去儲氣<br />\n<br />\n街霸比賽常見Term:<br />\nFootsie/Zoning = 立回 (因為隻GAME入面好多時D人用腳打人,因為遠Range)<br />\nSPD = Spinning Pile Driver(蘇聯代專用技,亦即係轉一圈個搖捍)<br />\nSBK= Chun Li's Spinning Bird Kick.<br />\nDP= Dragon Punch(昇龍拳)<br />\nAnti-air,Upper Cut=對空技.<br />\nCrush Counter = 今集新系統,由重拳,重腳引發既COUNTER稱為Crush Counter<br />\nChip damage=擋左既DAMAGE<br />\nBeast=野獸 (daigo既成名句,即係話你好似野獸一樣咁兇惡)<br />\nRead = 睇穿晒對手<br />\nDownload Complete = 都係睇穿晒對手既意思(不過比較串既意思,小心真人街霸)<br />\njab=輕拳<br />\nParry=擋走(Ryu vskill,Zangif vsill, Alex Vt等等)<br />\nFuzzy Guard =打頭技(中文暫時未清楚,唔明可以睇以下影片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3dH5feMgIgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3dH5feMgIgQ&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=311f0c56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3dH5feMgIgQ</a><br />\n各個高手的直播時間表<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eventhubs.com/streams/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eventhubs.com%2Fstreams%2F&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=3cc8b042\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eventhubs.com/streams/</a><br />\n各個大制資料<br />\n<a href=\"http://pcm.my-magazine.me/main/News/14727-a&amp;#138;Street+Fighter+Va&amp;#139;a&amp;#160;&amp;#188;e&amp;#172;￥e&amp;#129;&amp;#138;a&amp;#136;2a&amp;#137;&amp;#139;a&amp;#142;￡aa￠e&amp;#150;&plusmn;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpcm.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2FNews%2F14727-a%C2%80%26%23138%3BStreet%2BFighter%2BVa%C2%80%26%23139%3Ba%26%23160%3B%26%23188%3Be%26%23172%3B%EF%BF%A5e%26%23129%3B%26%23138%3Ba%26%23136%3B2a%26%23137%3B%26%23139%3Ba%26%23142%3B%EF%BF%A1aa%EF%BF%A0e%26%23150%3B%C2%B1&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8195c7c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://pcm.my-magazine.me/main/News/14727-a&amp;#138;Street+Fighter+Va&amp;#139;a&amp;#160;&amp;#188;e&amp;#172;￥e&amp;#129;&amp;#138;a&amp;#136;2a&amp;#137;&amp;#139;a&amp;#142;￡aa￠e&amp;#150;&plusmn;</a><br />\n街霸V資料 (暫時無乜野,本人得閒就會加野上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0BwT2DUE4mqG-OHltbzJRakt1d28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F0BwT2DUE4mqG-OHltbzJRakt1d28&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=f046cd9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0BwT2DUE4mqG-OHltbzJRakt1d28</a><br />\n街霸V WIKI<br />\n<a href=\"http://sfv-wiki.com/wiki/STREET_FIGHTER_V_Wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsfv-wiki.com%2Fwiki%2FSTREET_FIGHTER_V_Wiki&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=43c6fac4\" target=\"_blank\">http://sfv-wiki.com/wiki/STREET_FIGHTER_V_Wiki</a><br />\nFrame表:<br />\n比較建議手機DOWNLOAD一個APP叫Vframe,好實用.<br />\n<br />\nQ.總共角色數?<br />\nA.現階段為23個,<br />\n每一個角色為10萬GAME錢,或者6蚊美金<br />\n場地為7萬Game錢一個<br />\n<br />\n[size=6][red]Q.如果無香港國旗但又擇錯左國旗點算?<br />\nA.現階段無,到Season2都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55543304464ba86eed8f8f31c49e81335f642940","tid":54041,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連技小技巧</span></span><br />\n如何CHOK招駁大絕簡易方法(只限近攻情況) <br />\n有好多新手巴打經常遇到問題 <br />\n例如點樣CHOK昇,又或者如何CHOK波 <br />\n呢個係個小簡介. <br />\n有大部份人誤解左昇龍拳/波動拳 駁大絕 <br />\n係623拳/236拳236236拳 <br />\n其實唔需要咁樣做. <br />\n因為只要係發動大絕其間CHOK晒指令 <br />\n就算係中間加拳或者腳你都可以CHOK到大絕 <br />\n所以話 <br />\n如果你做 623拳/236拳,之後只需要禁236拳,你就駁到大絕. <br />\n整個流程係623拳236拳 或者 236拳236拳就可以做到晒. <br />\n唔需要623拳236236拳,因為咁會有機會造成MISS COMBO既情況. <br />\n只會不得嘗失. <br />\nCammy 236腳同623腳都可以做到同樣野. <br />\nKen可以 236拳236腳<br />\nNASH輕腳刀可以<br />\n但中腳刀時間有D慢,唔可以用以上方法.<br />\n一定要214中腳214214拳.<br />\n印度佬可以<br />\n其他情況就等你試下. <br />\n應該唔會有任何變化.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">高登Whatapp group</div></span></span><br />\n聯絡方法:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">WTapp GP:只要PM我留電話,我就可以拉你入Group,方便搵人對戰</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">P.S.:因為人數好多,入左Group之後耗電量會大增,所以請安裝省電App應付<br />\n而且,請將鈴聲較為無聲因為呢個Group24小時都會</span>有人<br />\n如果你唔想加入GP但又想同巴打玩,我已經係GOOGLE Drive個表到留晒所有巴打資料<br />\n就可以隨時同佢地打<br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/g95rtu82\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg95rtu82&h=95bfa4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/5x3plt84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5x3plt84&h=4f2c8cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://i.giphy.com/26ufdJgljD4wNRAze.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F26ufdJgljD4wNRAze.gif&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=6db18fd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://i.giphy.com/26ufdJgljD4wNRAze.gif</a><br />\n[/url]<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/hk9uppercut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fhk9uppercut&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=f0879421\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/hk9uppercut</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk9uppercut.wixsite.com/mysite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk9